{"Name":"River Valley Green (Parcel C)","ShortName":"River Valley Green (Parcel C)","Description":"Located right next to Great World MRT on the Thomson-East Coast Line, River Valley Green (Parcel C) presents a highly coveted city-fringe address. The 99-year leasehold site spans 123,964 sq ft with a maximum GFA of 433,882 sq ft, offering an estimated 470 new homes. ","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/6eb118dd-623e-4541-b5c3-f16a455b52d4","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/6eb118dd-623e-4541-b5c3-f16a455b52d4","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}